Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:15.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:22.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:34.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:39.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:45.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:50.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:01.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:07.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:13.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:18.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:24.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:28.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:15.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果將來能和你一起實現那永恆的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:22.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能夠變強 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:34.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有預告的奇跡邂逅 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:39.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守護你 再也不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:45.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:50.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:55.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證 一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:01.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法觸及的明天 高高在上無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:07.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的現實讓願望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:13.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恆的夢中期盼光明來臨的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:18.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會到達那裏 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:24.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:28.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我將與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:16.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:22.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:35.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:41.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:46.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:52.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:56.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:03.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:07.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:14.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:18.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:24.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:27.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:30.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:32.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:16.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠守護你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:22.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變得更強大 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:35.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓心情馳騁起來 超越各種危機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:41.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會馬上就讓你覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:46.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,曖昧弱小的心需要超越極限的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:52.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能捕捉到你的信號 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:56.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比誰都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:03.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情不斷高漲 來吧 用這個心情去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:07.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:14.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓一定用這雙手來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:18.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你拭去所有的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:24.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好擔心啊 但是你的笑容又讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:27.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:30.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:32.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更強更強 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是走這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有變..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒變呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 深山裏面有澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫做溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.08,0:01:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼意思啊 花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺行的嘛 葉太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一起來泡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要一起泡啦 我們就是為此而來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.78,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你們說會在房間裏休息一下我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼直勾勾地看著人家啊 葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}滑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳 吃早餐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯了哦 玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你知道我在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是玉鳳的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒在哪裏我當然知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪裏了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子雖然有些嚇人 但不可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓玉鳳和大家成為朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一家人不能好好相處 我做母親的很掛心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 葉太郎為什麼受了那樣的傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這件事 想讓一家人更親近..該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大家一起去大浴池泡澡就能增進感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和愛麗絲也是因為互相擦背才變得親近起來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家一起去溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼葉太郎不一起泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明白姬也都一起泡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為葉太郎大人是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是騎士部的合宿嘛 要講究女士優先的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 這同時也是騎士部的合宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須借助大自然的鍛煉讓葉太郎煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你按摩吧 冴醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我會幫你沖背的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為之前我們的家人讓你受驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不會..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了賠罪 我們會好好地服侍你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這怎麼行 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請儘管放鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就變得更親近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話玉鳳也..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼？玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一起來泡澡的話怎麼跟大家增進感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 害羞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 玉鳳 我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把真緒小姐對你的關心統統白費嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}蜻蜓切之間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那個小不點葉太郎居然長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到千代子小姐精神依舊真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是錦醬在的話她也會開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在去了外國的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看上去沒變 其實變了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好大的猴子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是..玉鳳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一起來泡澡的話怎麼跟大家增進感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個女孩子怎麼能穿成這樣跑來跑去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎麼了？玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點傷算什麼 一定要追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎很沒用 必須幫助他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳完全沒有察覺到我就是KnightLancer麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之你先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在對玉鳳做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？還能做什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 我在幫她穿衣服..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳 我說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒身在何處做母親的當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不是的 我什麼都沒有..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.58,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}庫洛倫內外藥品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想和大家一起泡澡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人..少了..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這是冴醬專用葉太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓他怎麼伺候你都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伺候..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓你做這種變態的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是玩這種COSPLAY..就是戴上面具..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替希露比亞她們向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們沒有惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎之事真的讓她們覺得愧對於你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在生花房君的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太善良總是被身邊的人支來使去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還為了我遭遇了那麼危險的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer就是花房君吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer..就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士什麼的..世上居然還存在著這樣一群人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 騎士在日本是匿名行事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以為了不被發現才戴面具？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士道體質這種詞 我也從來沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我曾因為這個而被人討厭過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 在這裏..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這樣的事..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後 我便開始想成為普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 讓冴同學經歷了好幾次不愉快的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..已經不能出現在冴同學的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校也..不能去了 然後..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君你說過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那句話是謊話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就別說什麼要退學的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一樣..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做回像往常一樣的..花房君..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛才說過你想成為普通人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學的話讓我很開心 結果騎士道體質不小心發作了..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止 總之今後變態行為要禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態行為..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如戴面具 或者親..親吻女生的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有扮COSPLAY..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴上這麼說 其實心裏很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你快被我親到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..你們在幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 因為希露比亞說最好能在戀愛上幫你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太遲鈍得很 有我們幫忙保證成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起破壞了溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀..沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再修好就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起讓你帶傷追趕我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起讓你受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起讓你害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳想成為好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為好孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓KnightLancer來到她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她之所以不願泡溫泉是因為KnightLancer不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說沒有KnightLancer的話就算不上「全家人好好相處」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳她正在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer一定也看在眼裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為好孩子..和爸爸一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子..成為好孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳 把爸爸刺傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是好孩子哦 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把這裏變為溫泉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer 果然是玉鳳的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也進來泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以偷偷離開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道就好 KnightLancer來了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下全家人就親密無間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 為什麼變態氣息更甚於前了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為..那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在發什麼呆 來嘛 冴也脫衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 大家都脫光光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全家人一起好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害羞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來嘛 別這麼不合群啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 今天是例外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 今天就當例外一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來泡溫泉真是來對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放鬆哦 葉太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回到家之前這都是騎士部的合宿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是讓我來拿自己的行李吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒..我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎..不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是全家人一起開心泡澡 葉太郎卻不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 花房君已經..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我已經..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡澡..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多泡一次也沒差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 又要泡澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 只有今天是例外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:09.97,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}只有今天是特例哦！
